<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Your Prescription is Ready</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      .container {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .logo {
        height: 60px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .status {
        background: #28a745;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .prescription-details {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
      }
      .medication-list {
        background: #fff3cd;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      }
      .medication-item {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      }
      .medication-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #2563eb;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6c757d;
      }
      .warning {
        background: #f8d7da;
        color: #721c24;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="cid:logo" alt="Online Consultation System" class="logo" />
        <h1>Your Prescription is Ready! üíä</h1>
        <div class="status">Prescription Generated</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{patientName}},</p>
        
        <p>Your prescription has been successfully generated by <strong>Dr. {{doctorName}}</strong> following your recent consultation.</p>

        <div class="prescription-details">
          <h3>üìã Prescription Details</h3>
          <p><strong>Prescription ID:</strong> #{{prescriptionId}}</p>
          <p><strong>Doctor:</strong> Dr. {{doctorName}}</p>
          {{#if diagnosis}}
          <p><strong>Diagnosis:</strong> {{diagnosis}}</p>
          {{/if}}
          <p><strong>Generated on:</strong> {{formatDate createdAt}}</p>
        </div>

        {{#if medications}}
        <div class="medication-list">
          <h3>üíä Prescribed Medications</h3>
          {{#each medications}}
          <div class="medication-item">
            <strong>{{this.name}}</strong>
            {{#if this.dosage}}<br><em>Dosage:</em> {{this.dosage}}{{/if}}
            {{#if this.frequency}}<br><em>Frequency:</em> {{this.frequency}}{{/if}}
            {{#if this.duration}}<br><em>Duration:</em> {{this.duration}}{{/if}}
          </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="warning">
          <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Instructions:</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>Please follow the prescribed dosage and frequency exactly as instructed</li>
            <li>Do not stop taking medication without consulting your doctor</li>
            <li>Contact your doctor immediately if you experience any adverse effects</li>
            <li>Keep all medications out of reach of children</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>You can view and download your complete prescription from your consultation details in the patient portal.</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Prescription in Portal</a>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions about your prescription or treatment, please don't hesitate to contact Dr. {{doctorName}} or our support team.</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing our Online Consultation System for your healthcare needs.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br />
        <strong>The Online Consultation Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from Online Consultation System.</p>
        <p>Please do not reply to this email. For support, contact our help desk.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Online Consultation System. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
